{
  "page": "Shrouded Lord",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">The Shrouded Lord</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Aliases</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>His Grey Grace</li><li>Prince of Sorrows</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Garin_the_Great\" title=\"Garin the Great\">Garin the Great</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stone_men\" title=\"Stone men\">Stone men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Shrouded Lord</b>, also known as <b>His Grey Grace</b> and the <b>Prince of Sorrows</b>, is a mysterious figure said to inhabit the <a href=\"/index.php/Sorrows\" title=\"Sorrows\">Sorrows</a>.  Many say he is just a legend.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrouded_Lord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Shrouded Lord is said to rule the mists around the <a href=\"/index.php/Sorrows\" title=\"Sorrows\">Sorrows</a> since the time of <a href=\"/index.php/Garin_(Prince)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Garin (Prince)\">Garin</a> and to spread <a href=\"/index.php/Greyscale\" title=\"Greyscale\">greyscale</a> through <i>the grey kiss</i>, although he does not bestow his kiss lightly according to <a href=\"/index.php/Haldon\" title=\"Haldon\">Haldon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to some rumors, he is thought to be Prince Garin himself, risen from his watery grave. Others believe that there have been numerous Shrouded Lords, and when one dies another one takes his place; the one currently holding the title is a <a href=\"/index.php/Corsair\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Corsair\">corsair</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Isles\" title=\"Basilisk Isles\">Basilisk Isles</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Rolly_Duckfield\" title=\"Rolly Duckfield\">Rolly Duckfield</a> likes yet another version of the tale, in which the Shrouded Lord was a statue at first, and a grey woman from the fog kissed life to it with lips as cold as ice.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> They say the Shrouded Lord will grant a boon to any man who can make him laugh.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> According to Septa <a href=\"/index.php/Lemore\" title=\"Lemore\">Lemore</a> the stone men were proud, and the Shrouded Lord was the proudest of all.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrouded_Lord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrouded_Lord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>As the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Shy_Maid\" title=\"Shy Maid\">Shy Maid</a></i> and her crew travel on the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> discussion turns to the Shrouded Lord and the various tales about him. <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> comes to associate the Shrouded Lord with <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, the father he slew, and has bad dreams of both.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrouded_Lord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>He dreamt of his lord father and the Shrouded Lord.  He dreamt that they were one and the same, and when his father wrapped stone arms around him and bent to give him his grey kiss, he woke with his mouth dry and rusty with the taste of blood and his heart hammering in his chest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> awakening from his near drowning</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Beyond the veil of dream, the <a href=\"/index.php/Sorrows\" title=\"Sorrows\">Sorrows</a> were waiting for him.  Stone steps ascending endlessly, steep and slick and treacherous, and somewhere at the top, the Shrouded Lord.  <b>I do not want to meet the Shrouded Lord</b>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>, drunk in a <a href=\"/index.php/Selhorys\" title=\"Selhorys\">Selhorys</a> brothel</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shrouded_Lord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, Tyrion V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_22\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 22\">Chapter 22</a>, Tyrion VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403213501\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.098 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.311 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 984/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10674/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6576/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1175/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2522/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  301.751      1 -total\n 92.32%  278.570      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 91.52%  276.173      1 Template:Infobox\n 13.79%   41.607     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  6.27%   18.932      7 Template:Ref\n  4.15%   12.521      7 Template:Ref/core\n  3.34%   10.090      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.26%    3.790      2 Template:Quote\n  0.84%    2.541      1 Template:References\n  0.43%    1.287      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:7438-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403213500 and revision id 318551\n -->\n",
